    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/5110ce462895aae7f6f2b4a418b0179f.poster.avif?t=1758530488\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/5110ce462895aae7f6f2b4a418b0179f.webm?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/5110ce462895aae7f6f2b4a418b0179f.mp4?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BERSERKER'S DOMAIN</strong> 狂战之境是一款快节奏、狂野的复古第一人称射击游戏，采用 Roguelike 循环玩法。灵感来源于经典游戏 <i>Blood</i>、<i>Quake 1-3</i> 和 <i>Doom</i>、以及现代射击游戏 Dusk、<i>ULTRAKILL</i> 和 <i>Doom Eternal</i>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已经死了——但随即被释放到一个充满极端暴力、爆炸、肢体横飞、欢乐和新鲜猎物的来世！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/9e590810d01bf46a9a3ab8b990600749.poster.avif?t=1758530488\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/9e590810d01bf46a9a3ab8b990600749.webm?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/9e590810d01bf46a9a3ab8b990600749.mp4?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以极快的速度在战场上奔跑、冲刺和二段跳，撕碎成群的邪教徒、恶魔、怪物、士兵、术士和半神。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挥舞一系列残暴的武器，每种武器都有各种不合常理的升级选项。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁终极&quot;协同升级&quot;，组合不同武器的加成效果。想要一个爆炸后射出霰弹的炸药？当然可以。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/aa6e10302441a835085b65e04f57ac99.poster.avif?t=1758530488\" width=616 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/aa6e10302441a835085b65e04f57ac99.webm?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277520/extras/aa6e10302441a835085b65e04f57ac99.mp4?t=1758530488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按下开始按钮，5秒内即可开始射击。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有菜单，没有加载界面，没有教程。运行游戏即可畅玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次死亡都会开启一个全新的随机关卡，带来新的地图、武器、升级和敌人。每次游戏体验都独一无二。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奔跑。猎杀。暴走</strong></p>",
